<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="id">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Album Spesial Cia</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Dancing+Script:wght@700&family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        * {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            box-sizing: border-box;
        }

        body {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffdde1 0%, #ee9ca7 100%);
            min-height: 100vh;
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            overflow-x: hidden;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 40px 20px;
        }

        /* Latar belakang animasi hati */
        .hearts {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100%;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        .heart {
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -100px;
            background-color: #ffb6c1;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            transform: rotate(-45deg);
            animation: float 6s ease-in infinite;
            opacity: 0.6;
        }

        .heart::before, .heart::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            width: 20px;
            height: 20px;
            background-color: #ffb6c1;
            border-radius: 50%;
        }

        .heart::before { top: -10px; left: 0; }
        .heart::after { left: 10px; top: 0; }

        /* Variasi animasi hati */
        .heart:nth-child(1) { left: 10%; animation-duration: 5s; animation-delay: 0s; }
        .heart:nth-child(2) { left: 30%; animation-duration: 7s; animation-delay: 2s; }
        .heart:nth-child(3) { left: 50%; animation-duration: 6s; animation-delay: 1s; }
        .heart:nth-child(4) { left: 70%; animation-duration: 8s; animation-delay: 3s; }
        .heart:nth-child(5) { left: 90%; animation-duration: 5.5s; animation-delay: 0.5s; }

        @keyframes float {
            0% { transform: translateY(0) rotate(-45deg) scale(0.8); opacity: 0; }
            50% { opacity: 0.8; }
            100% { transform: translateY(-1000px) rotate(-45deg) scale(1.2); opacity: 0; }
        }

        /* Kontainer Utama */
        .container {
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
            text-align: center;
            max-width: 900px;
            animation: fadeIn 2s ease-in-out;
        }

        @keyframes fadeIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(-20px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }

        .message-box {
            background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85);
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 20px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 30px rgba(238, 156, 167, 0.4);
            margin-bottom: 50px;
            border: 2px solid #ffb6c1;
        }

        .message-box h1 {
            font-family: 'Dancing Script', cursive;
            color: #d84384;
            font-size: 2.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 15px;
        }

        .message-box p {
            color: #555;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .sender {
            margin-top: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #d84384;
        }

        /* Galeri Polaroid */
        .gallery {
            display: flex;
            flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 30px;
        }

        .polaroid {
            background: white;
            padding: 15px 15px 40px 15px;
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: all 0.4s ease;
            position: relative;
            width: 250px;
        }

        .polaroid img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 250px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border: 1px solid #eee;
        }

        /* Rotasi acak untuk efek berantakan yang estetik */
        .polaroid:nth-child(odd) { transform: rotate(-5deg); }
        .polaroid:nth-child(even) { transform: rotate(5deg); }
        .polaroid:nth-child(3) { transform: rotate(-3deg); }

        .polaroid:hover {
            transform: scale(1.1) rotate(0deg);
            box-shadow: 0 15px 30px rgba(238, 156, 167, 0.6);
            z-index: 10;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="hearts">
        <div class="heart"></div>
        <div class="heart"></div>
        <div class="heart"></div>
        <div class="heart"></div>
        <div class="heart"></div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="message-box">
            <h1>CIA ADALAH BEST FRIEND TERBAIK SAYA</h1>
            <p>Semoga selalu jadi best friend yah! ❤️</p>
            <p class="sender">- Zildjian</p>
        </div>

        <div class="gallery">
            <div class="polaroid">
                <img src="https://autoresbot.com/tmp_files/7572ebbd-8fc6-4b43-a4bd-11d62b2533e5.jpg" alt="Cia 1">
            </div>
            <div class="polaroid">
                <img src="https://autoresbot.com/tmp_files/592d2d16-a961-461e-a4f1-db429df8b879.jpg" alt="Cia 2">
            </div>
            <div class="polaroid">
                <img src="https://autoresbot.com/tmp_files/2d1e2a81-6d56-41bd-8b27-1492b208888e.jpg" alt="Cia 3">
            </div>
            <div class="polaroid">
                <img src="https://autoresbot.com/tmp_files/d9947d3c-9c78-43c8-ad65-239d6f0e8830.jpg" alt="Cia 4">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

</body>
</html>
